.TH "atc_tx_status" 9 "atc_tx_status" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
atc_tx_status \- poll for transaction completion
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "enum dma_status" atc_tx_status
.BI "(struct dma_chan *chan "  ","
.BI "dma_cookie_t cookie "  ","
.BI "struct dma_tx_state *txstate "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "chan" 12
DMA channel
.IP "cookie" 12
transaction identifier to check status of
.IP "txstate" 12
if not NULL updated with transaction state
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
If \fItxstate\fP is passed in, upon return it reflect the driver
internal state and can be used with \fBdma_async_is_complete\fP to check
the status of multiple cookies without re-checking hardware state.
